name: Integrity Human Development Foundation
briefDescription: Integrity Human Development Foundation (IHDF) is Voluntary Organization has been working for the Human Development through out the activities for Women and Tribal people from the hilly area of “Satpuda”. Now IHDF is Registered Organization on 17th of March 2010, has completed 3rd year of achievement with sense of pride and satisfaction is a non profit, non-Governmental Organization dedicated to its mission to serve the Rural Community poor and downtrodden.  During this period the Organization has developed its own distinctive identity and is always sensitive to the needs of the project area.Organization has covered 4560 Male, 2272 Female, 670 Children and 9700 Landless and Farmer benificiaries throughout the implementation of program.
